<br>
As for manaburn.. sure, it can be taken advantage of and used unfairly, but so can a lot of other things in game.  (Yes, I am a mb wiz on RZ).<br>
<br>
Bottom line is that it's up to you to defend yourself.. you play on RZ after all.  You should always be aware of your surroundings and prepared to fight at all times.  Sometimes you're not going to have a chance to win the fight, but that's just the way it is, and that happens to all classes (trust me, it happens to wizards all the time).  PvP has a lot to do with luck in EQ, always has been.  Sure, with better gear, lvl, and skill you improve (sometimes drastically) your odds, but it still boils down to how much will this spell hit for, or how much will my melee do.<br>
<br>
Mach <p><TABLE BORDER=0><TR><TD>
